{"tid":310190,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(求有志之士一齊組隊)Escape From Tarkov 小眾第一人稱PC擬真向生存遊戲","createTime":"2017-07-05T15:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:15:20.000Z","uid":80473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2054b5c9cf9a68bc859387f0e712a3f17fbe5af6","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/uploads/content/news/content_thumb_e0e4527ae0c255a6aa0dffbc0cd83430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2Fuploads%2Fcontent%2Fnews%2Fcontent_thumb_e0e4527ae0c255a6aa0dffbc0cd83430.jpg&h=fa7406af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/uploads/filemanager/files/shorelinenew/eft_shoreline_wip2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2Fuploads%2Ffilemanager%2Ffiles%2Fshorelinenew%2Feft_shoreline_wip2_1.jpg&h=5d8045be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/uploads/filemanager/files/shorelinenew/eft_shoreline_wip2_10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2Fuploads%2Ffilemanager%2Ffiles%2Fshorelinenew%2Feft_shoreline_wip2_10.jpg&h=9a9a790a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/uploads/filemanager/files/hideout/escapefromtarkov_hideout20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2Fuploads%2Ffilemanager%2Ffiles%2Fhideout%2Fescapefromtarkov_hideout20.jpg&h=03dd5270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰鬥民族工作室出的PC GAME, 可以睇下佢個CG宣傳片先:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8R5t3a2jT4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8R5t3a2jT4A&d=z6YGOoPics3UQNwnEk9m4C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1935cac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8R5t3a2jT4A</a><br />\n<br />\ngameplay:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7A5DXxgBZkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7A5DXxgBZkM&d=z6YGOoPics3UQNwnEk9m4C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dc3b3184\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7A5DXxgBZkM</a><br />\n<br />\n而家隻GAME仲測試緊, 不過睇佢而家的進度我覺得未來會係一隻正GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n官網:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2F&d=z6YGOoPics3UQNwnEk9m4C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=597d3c33\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.escapefromtarkov.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生存類遊戲單機好易出事, 希望揾幾個志同道合的人留低TG一齊組隊玩<br />\n<br />\n雖然我啱啱先開始玩, 但係有咩問題可以試下問我"},{"pid":"f55e8baafe64a32b3b8894dcc0cfecf623e97796","tid":310190,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:03:49.000Z","msg":"同同類game有冇乜分別或特色？"},{"pid":"fcfa10e24f5289f010b3394cc603b310b5e520c7","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T22:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同同類game有冇乜分別或特色？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5649bbe2695ce144272b2cb44f653805f6a0b57b","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T22:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同同類game有冇乜分別或特色？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真實向丶軍事味更濃丶節奏慢<br />\n例如一把槍每一個位都可以定制, 可以換唔同的零件, 什至槍管丶槍托都有得換<br />\n換彈夾都有兩種模式, 一種係會回收返個彈夾, 另一種係扔低個彈夾落地去換取更快的reload速度"},{"pid":"4215beb7283c99080bccd0dab19665314bb1cbdf","tid":310190,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"好期待<br />\n但唔知幾時先有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04342b2bb28780c2ea65f80e2c93b4fb598e376a","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好期待<br />\n但唔知幾時先有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家都有得玩，最貴果個版本100%玩到，其他版本有一定機率玩到<br />\n佢今個月會入close beta，所有pre order左佢隻game的人都會玩到"},{"pid":"f9b068ea9cc29a3da40890f31d449551668ae40f","tid":310190,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同同類game有冇乜分別或特色？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真實向丶軍事味更濃丶節奏慢<br />\n例如一把槍每一個位都可以定制, 可以換唔同的零件, 什至槍管丶槍托都有得換<br />\n換彈夾都有兩種模式, 一種係會回收返個彈夾, 另一種係扔低個彈夾落地去換取更快的reload速度</blockquote><br />\n太真實向未必會好玩左<br />\n每樣野都煩左等耐左<br />\n<br />\n其實好似L4D咁誇張爽快已經好好玩<br />\n遊戲性/娛樂性高<br />\n有時好過真實性高<br />\n遊戲始終係娛樂為主導<br />\n下下學真實世界咁煩就不如唔好打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5abc689e83581eedd1f9324ad437e108276e017","tid":310190,"uid":28814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"PUBG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9e5f305fedcc1891c47c76343ba41466385139","tid":310190,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PUBG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻畫質都好過佢"},{"pid":"601a62c17384b0a2bb0dff50883e69b237b90a1f","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同同類game有冇乜分別或特色？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真實向丶軍事味更濃丶節奏慢<br />\n例如一把槍每一個位都可以定制, 可以換唔同的零件, 什至槍管丶槍托都有得換<br />\n換彈夾都有兩種模式, 一種係會回收返個彈夾, 另一種係扔低個彈夾落地去換取更快的reload速度</blockquote><br />\n太真實向未必會好玩左<br />\n每樣野都煩左等耐左<br />\n<br />\n其實好似L4D咁誇張爽快已經好好玩<br />\n遊戲性/娛樂性高<br />\n有時好過真實性高<br />\n遊戲始終係娛樂為主導<br />\n下下學真實世界咁煩就不如唔好打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各有所好<br />\n唔係人人都鐘意無腦射<br />\n不一定要有娛樂性先有樂趣<br />\n例如:模擬飛行X"},{"pid":"077029d19c0dba3c49abe1c6f118e7ae9aea8793","tid":310190,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/etwETB-IaMs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https